Alice, Bob, Claire, Dave, and Eve are friends and avid readers who occasionally trade books. At the start of the semester, they each buy one new book: Alice gets The Odyssey, Bob gets Moby Dick, Claire gets Lolita, Dave gets The Fellowship of the Ring, and Eve gets Frankenstein.
As the semester proceeds, they start trading around the new books. First, Eve and Bob swap books. Then, Dave and Alice swap books. Then, Dave and Bob swap books. Then, Bob and Claire swap books. Finally, Alice and Dave swap books. At the end of the semester, Eve has
Options:
(A) The Odyssey
(B) Moby Dick
(C) Lolita
(D) The Fellowship of the Ring
(E) Frankenstein
